---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Homage Index"
  description="Homage Index ranks luxury watch homages by visual similarity. Find the best homage for any luxury watch, with honest scoring and direct buy links."
>
  <div class="container about-wrap">
    <header class="about-header">
      <p class="t-label eyebrow">About this site</p>
      <h1 class="about-title">What is Homage Index?</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-body">
      <p>
        Homage Index is a curated directory of luxury watch homages, ranked by how visually
        similar they are to the originals that inspired them. Every pair includes a similarity
        score, a price comparison, and a direct link to buy.
      </p>
      <p>
        The similarity scores are editorial judgments based on dial design, case profile,
        hand set, bezel execution, and overall wrist presence — not automated. We try to
        be honest about where homages succeed and where they fall short.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site contains affiliate links. If you buy through one of our links, we may earn
        a small commission at no extra cost to you. This is how the site stays independent.
      </p>
      <p>
        Homage watches are legal, distinct from counterfeits, and a legitimate way to enjoy
        iconic watch designs. We do not list or link to replica or counterfeit watches.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.about-wrap {
  max-width: 640px;
  padding-top: 3rem;
  padding-bottom: 4rem;
}

.eyebrow {
  color: var(--color-ink-faint);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.about-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: normal;
  font-variant-numeric: lining-nums;
  color: var(--color-ink);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  line-height: 1.15;
}

.about-body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.25rem;
}

.about-body p {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--color-ink-muted);
}
</style>
